# GitNexus GenAnh Context

- This workspace is GenAnh, not TSS.
- When using GitNexus MCP tools, pass `repo: "hieuanhai"` unless user explicitly asks for another repo.
- GitNexus repo `hieuanhai` maps to `/home/chinhanh` on branch `main`.
- Do not omit `repo` for GitNexus queries because indexed TSS repos also exist.
- If GitNexus data seems stale, run from `/home/chinhanh/app`: `npx gitnexus analyze`.
